# Fishing
Fishing is a way to get renewable resources as well as a decent amount of food! It also has access to some items otherwise unavalible...


  <Box>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FishBass" Caption="REAL FISH"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FishTropical" Caption="REAL FISH"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FishFatFuckingCunt" Caption="STUPID"/>
  </Box>

# Getting Started
Start by getting a fishing rod. You can craft rods, or order them from cargo. Not all rods perform the same.

  <Box>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FishingRodMakeshift" Caption="Crafted rod"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FishingRod" Caption="Ordered rod"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FishingRodGolden" Caption="Secret rod..."/>
  </Box>

Once you have a rod, find a fishing spot. You can currently fish in the following structures:

  <Box>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="WaterFishingPool" Caption="Ordered from cargo"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="LavaFishingPool" Caption="Ordered from cargo"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="PlasmaFishingPool" Caption="Ordered from cargo"/>
  </Box>
  <Box>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FloorWaterEntity" Caption="Found Nautrally"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FloorLavaEntity" Caption="Found Nautrally"/>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="FloorLiquidPlasmaEntity" Caption="Found Nautrally"/>
  </Box>
  <Box>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="ToiletDirtyWater" Caption="Ew!"/>
  </Box>

# Minigame

Once you hook a fish, spam the "Z" button to reel it in! It's that simple.

  <Box>
    <GuideEntityEmbed Entity="BloodWritingZ" Caption="This is what the letter Z looks like."/>
  </Box>

# Loot

Every fishing spot has different loot to get, most will give you fish, but some have special secret items or other useful things. Make sure to butcher rare fish to extract their special items!

